Dear Hiring Team, 

It is with great pleasure that I submit my candidacy for the *Software Engineer* position with *Genesis Capital*. I bring over three years of professional experience in full-stack development, cloud-native architectures, and AI-ready systems, along with a strong academic foundation as a Master of Science in Computer Science graduate from Pace University, NY.

